## Ignore VS temporary files, some build results and files generated by popular VS add-ons

# Blender files
*.blend

# User-specific file
*.suo
*.VC.db
*.opendb

# Visual Studio cache/options directory
.vs/

# Temporary Debug/Release folders
OpenGLProject/Intermediate/

# Debug build files
Output/Debug

# Unnecessary release build files
Output/Release/**/*.iobj
Output/Release/**/*.ipdb
Output/Release/**/*.pdb

# Sciencific research papers
Documents
